The paper deals with image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves optimizing the mean average precision (mAP) using listwise loss formulations, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of deep models, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL) research.
